  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Efficacy and tolerance of Tegeline® treatment in hypersensitivity syndrome. Immunological
      study of the T cell index phenotype and functionality in hypersensitivity syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
